For some things it's nice to be able to go back and insert new ideas, edit, etc.  For others it's definitely simpler to use pen and paper.  My biggest complaint with the android device is having each app so isolated from each other...it's hard to pass along a document from one to the other.  I want to think that Github or git alone is enough, I guess google or dropbox should work also.


